{"id": "art-1251", "label": "Art. 1251", "title": "Art. 1251", "slug": "art-1251", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2068401155\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2296\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2068401155\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u><span style='color:#569748'>Art. 125<sup>1</sup></span></u></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_60919595\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2295\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_60919595\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span>, în\npersoan&#259; sau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>, pot participa <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> vota fizic sau prin mijloace electronice de\ncomunicare la <span class=SpellE>distan&#355;&#259;</span> în cadrul\nadun&#259;rilor generale potrivit alin. (2). <span class=SpellE>Ace&#351;tia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> pot exprima votul <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nprin <span class=SpellE>coresponden&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1715385167\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2294\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1715385167\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(2)Dac&#259; actul constitutiv prevede sau dac&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> hot&#259;r&#259;sc astfel cu majoritatea\nprev&#259;zut&#259; de art. 115, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> pot\nparticipa la adunarea general&#259; prin mijloace electronice de comunicare la <span\nclass=SpellE>distan&#355;&#259;</span>, care trebuie s&#259; întruneasc&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> tehnice necesare pentru identificarea <span\nclass=SpellE>participan&#355;ilor</span>, pentru participarea efectiv&#259; a\nacestora <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> retransmiterea deliber&#259;rilor în\nmod continuu, pentru exercitarea dreptului <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nde a se adresa adun&#259;rii, pentru exprimarea votului, în cadrul\nadun&#259;rii generale, astfel încât s&#259; permit&#259; identificarea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, verificarea ulterioar&#259; a modului în\ncare s-a votat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> posibilitatea ca fiecare <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span> s&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\npoat&#259; verifica votul exprimat.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_518635870\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2293\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_518635870\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(3)Hot&#259;rârile adoptate în cadrul adun&#259;rii\ngenerale <span class=SpellE>desf&#259;&#351;urate</span> în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (2) se semneaz&#259; olograf sau cu\nsemn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259;, în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\n<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>.</span></u><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}